General.Name: Panostaja Oyj
General.Description: Panostaja Oyj is a private equity firm specializing in investments in expansions through corporate acquisitions, industry consolidations, and mature and middle market investments in small and medium-sized companies through acquisitions in sectors undergoing growth and restructuring. It focuses on those companies, which seek to execute a generational or majority owner. The firm invests in diverse sectors with a focus on communications, computer related and environmental technology, forest industry, energy, transportation, agriculture and tourism. The firm prefers to invest in Finland. It invests in companies with enterprise values between "5 million ($5.53 million) and "25 million ($27.65 million) and net sales between EUR 10 million ($11.06 million) and 30 million ($33.18 million). The firm takes majority stakes or buys the companies in entirety and exits the investments within five to ten years. The firm typically invests through balance sheet. Panostaja Oyj was founed in 1984 and is located in Tampere, Finland.
